# spec-guard IP firewall — keep the knowledge graph deliverable-only.
#
# The backup-monorepo root versions intellectual property that each deliverable's .gitignore
# excludes. graphify respects .gitignore, so a per-module build (cwd = module) stays IP-clean
# automatically — but a stray `graphify extract` AT THIS ROOT would index the IP below straight
# into the graph. The root graph must instead be a `graphify merge-graphs` of the clean per-module
# graphs (see docs/reference/decisions/0009-graph-topology-and-ip-firewall.md). This file is
# defense-in-depth for that rule.

# Internal IP knowledge base
${privateDir}/

# Per-agent integration / governance dirs (the IP tooling, never shipped)
.claude/
.codex/
.gemini/
.opencode/
.superpowers/
.spec-guard/
.github/copilot-instructions.md
.github/prompts/
.github/skills/

# Secrets / env / local credentials
.env
.env.*
*.local.md
**/secrets.*

# Database backups / scratch — never architectural signal
**/db-backups/
